body_html: "Prepare failed! returned 0xffffffff" means that it couldn't create NN in HVX. So, I assume there may be some incompatibility issues on your hardware. You may want to build nnlib by yourself for your hardware and that may work. This feature is pretty much frozen mode, so you may want to wait for tflite for better hardware supports.
